name: POWERSKULL_01 - Golden Time Cranium
description:
Master Alchemists of an ancient tribe from the extinct planet 396-Gamma were responsible for crafting all the POWERSKULLZ.

The Legends from the Great Elders describe how this Golden Time Cranium gave time-travelling abilities to whoever grabbed it with both hands and raised it to eye level.

This time-travel artefact would work only when held by a human being. The skull's resonant frequency is in tune with the electromagnetic field emanated by human beings. The electromagnetic field of the human carrying the Golden Time Cranium would make it self-oscillate in a feedback loop that causes a safe portal-in-time to open.

Other living forms' magnetic fields would not be tuned to the Golden Time Cranium and would not activate it.

The POWERSKULLZ are part of the POWERVERSE, a reality where humans have achieved their highest potential and live as gods.
